# Keep version-controlled scripts runnable on every host. Git for Windows' bundled
# bash cannot execute a script with CRLF endings, and cmd.exe control-flow blocks can
# break with LF endings, so pin each script type to the endings its interpreter needs.
* text=auto
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.ps1  text eol=lf
*.bat  text eol=crlf
*.cmd  text eol=crlf
.riprap/managed/hooks/* text eol=lf
